title: The Quick-Fix Home Organizer: Making Your Home Beautiful
description:
The Quick-Fix Home Organizer: Making Your Home Beautiful and Your Life Clutter Free by Emilie Barnes

Overview: Home management expert Emilie Barnes, whose books have sold more than 4.5 million copies, has a vast collection of home and life organization tips to share. The Quick-Fix Home Organizer is packed with brief, practical, and inspirational ideas to help readers create homes filled with peace and personality. Always warm and encouraging, Emilie motivates her readers to start and finish projects with success create a home that reflects personal style sort through and find the right place for piled-up papers, clothing, and toys add fun and function to each room get the most out of a daily planner By implementing these quick fixes, readers enjoy a more organized home and work space. They conserve their energy and discover more time to spend with family and friends
